        <abstract> 
<p>Believes his letter of 17 Apr bears also on vol. 1 of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Ability to move ears is common in his family.</p>
            <p>Similarity of foot of man to that of gorilla continues beyond foetal stage.</p>
            <p>Invites CD to stay overnight if visiting the area.</p>
